&lt;p>&lt;em>1. अजीर्णे भोजनं विषम् ।&lt;/em>
If previously taken Lunch is not digested..taking Dinner will be equivalent to taking Poison. Hunger is one signal that the previous food is digested&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;em>2. अर्धरोगहरी निद्रा ।&lt;/em>
Proper sleep cures half of the diseases..&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;em>3 मुद्गदाली गदव्याली ।&lt;/em>
Of all the Pulses, Green grams are the best. It boosts Immunity. Other Pulses all have one or the other side effects.&lt;/p></description></item></channel></rss>